short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: git lab project browser - browser extension

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you know the frustration of trying to get to a certain repo on
Gitlab, but you're not mananaging to find it through the maze of
Groups & Subgroups? This browser extension simply adds a button
to the menu which shows a list of all repo's you have access to.

Easy peasy.
